    <AbstractNarration>This is a proposal for a workshop on the emerging new area, Cloud Robotics. The integration of&lt;br/&gt;robots into the Cloud holds the promise of giving unprecedented computation and memory&lt;br/&gt;resources to the robots. In parallel, robots can augment Cloud applications by giving them the&lt;br/&gt;power to collect data on demand.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;The workshop will bring together robotics, cloud computing and big-data researches to explore&lt;br/&gt;the opportunities and challenges in Cloud Robotics.</AbstractNarration>
